nm:output.nm:control_stream:
$PROB PK1 $INPUT ID TIME AMT DV EVID WT0 AGE0 SEX STUD $DATA ../../Data/data_pk.csv IGNORE=@ $SUBROUTINE ADVAN13 TOL=3 $MODEL NCOMPS=2 $PK KA =THETA(1)*EXP(ETA(1)) V = THETA(2)*EXP(ETA(2))*(WT0/75)**THETA(4) CL =THETA(3)*EXP(ETA(3))*(WT0/75)**THETA(5)*(AGE0/45)**THETA(6)*EXP(LOG(THETA(7))*SEX)*EXP(LOG(THETA(8))*(STUD-1))
$DES DADT(1) = -KA*A(1) DADT(2) = KA*A(1) - CL/V*A(2) $THETA 1 1 1 1 1 1 1 1 $OMEGA 0.01 0.01 0.01 $SIGMA 1 $ERROR IPRED = A(2)/V IWRES = DV-IPRED NPDE = DV-IPRED Y= IPRED * (1+EPS(1))
$ESTIMATION METHOD=1 INTERACTION PRINT=10 NOABORT POSTHOC MAXEVALS=9999 $COV $TABLE ID WT0 AGE0 SEX STUD ETA1 ETA2 ETA3 FILE=indiv_eta.txt $TABLE ID TIME IPRED PRED IWRES NPDE FILE=predictions.txt
